Before writing Expo code, read the exact Expo SDK 57 docs at `https://docs.expo.dev/versions/v57.0.0/`.

Rules:
- Use Expo Router file-based navigation.
- Keep bottom tabs named Feed, Browse, and Account; keep all routes aligned with `docs/USER_FLOWS.md`.
- Do not assume older Expo or Expo Router behavior; use the installed SDK versions in `package.json`.

Feature work follows the routine in `skills/feature-slice-builder/SKILL.md`.
